headline.main: SWEDEN RE-AVOWS HER INDEPENDENCE; Refusal to Aid Possible Nazi Move on Russia Hinted at by Premier Hansson HE BARS TIE WITH AXIS He and Other Ministers Speak in Country-Wide Demonstration of 'National Solidarity'

lead_paragraph: STOCKHOLM, Sweden, May 1 -- Almost a million Swedes throughout the country took part today in a demonstration of "national solidarity" under the motto of "freedom above everything, for him who is worthy of it."
